==English==

===Etymology===
[[outlie]] + [[-er]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A person or thing away from others or outside its [[proper]] [[place]].
# (''geology'') A [[part]] of a [[formation]] separated from the rest of the formation by [[erosion]].
# (''statistics'') A [[value]] in a [[statistical]] sample which does not fit a [[pattern]] that describes most other [[data]] [[point]]s.

